headline: Does Jabil’s (JBL) $1 Billion Refi Hint at a Sharper Balance-Sheet Playbook?
summary: In mid-January 2026, Jabil Inc. priced US$500,000,000 of 4.200% Senior Notes due 2029 and US$500,000,000 of 4.750% Senior Notes due 2033, planning to use part of the proceeds to repay its US$500,000,000 1.700% Senior Notes due 2026 and for general corporate purposes.
